{"word":"Purification","slug":"purification","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Purification</b> Sanitary and symbolic.<br/> For women:<br/> - Before marriage<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=12'>Est 2:12</a> <br/> - After childbirth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=12&verse=8'>Lev 12:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=22'>Luk 2:22</a> <br/> - After menstruation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=15&verse=33'>Lev 15:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=4'>2Sa 11:4</a> <br/> Of the Jews before the Passover<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=55'>Joh 11:55</a><br/> For those who have slain in battle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=24'>Num 31:24</a><br/> Of lepers<br/> <a href='S:Leprosy'>Leprosy</a><br/> by fire, for things that resist fire<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=23'>Num 31:23</a><br/> by blood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=8'>Exo 24:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=7'>Lev 14:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=14'>Heb 9:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=22'>Heb 9:22</a><br/> by abstaining from sexual intercourse<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=15'>Exo 19:15</a><br/> Washing in water, parts of animal sacrifices<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=1&verse=9'>Lev 1:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=1&verse=13'>Lev 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=9&verse=14'>Lev 9:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=4&verse=6'>2Ch 4:6</a><br/> Penalty to be imposed upon those who do not observe the ordinances concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=7&verse=21'>Lev 7:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=13'>Num 19:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=20'>Num 19:20</a><br/> Water of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=21'>Num 19:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=23'>Num 31:23</a><br/> Washing hands in water, symbolic of innocency<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=6'>Deu 21:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=26&verse=6'>Psa 26:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=24'>Mat 27:24</a><br/> Traditions of the elders concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=2'>Mat 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=5'>Mar 7:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=9'>Mar 7:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=11&verse=38'>Luk 11:38</a><br/> Of Paul, to show his fidelity to the law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=24'>Act 21:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=26'>Act 21:26</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=26&verse=6'>Psa 26:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=51&verse=7'>Psa 51:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=36&verse=25'>Eze 36:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=10&verse=22'>Heb 10:22</a><br/><a href='S:Ablution'>Ablution</a>; <a href='S:Defilement'>Defilement</a>; <a href='S:Sanitation'>Sanitation</a><br/> Scriptures relating to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=2'>Gen 35:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=10'>Exo 19:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=14'>Exo 19:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=4'>Exo 29:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=21'>Exo 30:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=12'>Exo 40:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=32'>Exo 40:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8&verse=6'>Lev 8:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=9'>Lev 14:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=15&verse=13'>Lev 15:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=15&verse=27'>Lev 15:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=4'>Lev 16:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=24'>Lev 16:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=26'>Lev 16:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=28'>Lev 16:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=15'>Lev 17:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=3'>Lev 22:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=7'>Num 8:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=21'>Num 8:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=8'>Num 19:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=19'>Num 19:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=4&verse=6'>2Ch 4:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=9'>Mar 7:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=2'>Mat 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse